<a href="/questions/819628-i-read-this-book-over-40-years-ago-so-i">I read this book over 40 years ago, so I don&#39;t remember much about it. It was during my &#39;Baldwin&#39; phase. I seemed to think i was more impressed with Giovanni&#39;s Room.&#39; With racial tension back in America, could his work be coming back into vogue ?</a>
