              <span id="reviewTextContainer1093331056" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14002248914142873683">I feel this one just wasn&apos;t for me. I didn&apos;t engage with this novel at all. I must say that it is written very well (obviously, it&apos;s Baldwin) but the overall story and characters didn&apos;t do much for me. I&apos;m kinda disappointed tbh, this is Baldwin&apos;s most popular novel according to Goodreads but I personally think that <i>Giovanni&apos;s Room</i> blows this one out of the water. </span>
  <span id="freeText14002248914142873683" style="display:none">I feel this one just wasn't for me. I didn't engage with this novel at all. I must say that it is written very well (obviously, it's Baldwin) but the overall story and characters didn't do much for me. I'm kinda disappointed tbh, this is Baldwin's most popular novel according to Goodreads but I personally think that <i>Giovanni's Room</i> blows this one out of the water. </span>
